{"tid":628836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警無歸還　錄影會面光碟不知所終","createTime":"2018-04-14T08:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T10:59:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd0f61a911151d89f0441f83a4a894c465f7d95","tid":628836,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361299?_ga=2.49384102.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361299%3F_ga%3D2.49384102.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=as0WiOeuhvz8opnM8qFyTwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=e22a708a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361299%3F_ga%3D2.49384102.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=71497fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361299?_ga=2.49384102.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n警無歸還　錄影會面光碟不知所終<br />\n<br />\n4.6K<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/14la3p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F14la3p6.jpg&h=127e5b7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁天琦昨被押往高院審訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【旺角騷亂案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】2016年大年初二旺角發生騷亂，本土民主前線梁天琦等多人被控煽惑暴動、參與暴動及非法集結罪昨高院續審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方下周完結舉證<br />\n<br />\n案件於今年2月正式開審，排期60日的審訊已進行了32日，控方昨日指只餘一名控方證人需要傳召，預計下周一便會完結控方案情，跟着會由辯方舉證。<br />\n<br />\n控方昨傳召參與拘捕第五被告的警員作供，辯方指有錄影會面光碟不知去向，而且警方威逼第五被告承認指控和按教導作供。<br />\n<br />\n第五被告林倫慶前年3月4日晚上被捕後，被押往青山和屯門警署進行了兩次錄影會面。行動中保管證物的警員周健邦昨供稱，每次會面錄影只需用一套光碟，為防機器故障他通常準備兩套；會面完畢後，警方會即場將錄影光碟放入防干擾膠袋保管。<br />\n<br />\n周確認為林的兩次會面提取共四套光碟，他稱只用了兩套，其餘兩套沒有歸還警方。他說警方沒指引要歸還未用的光碟，他沒考究原因，一般他會收藏在行動背囊或房間，惟現時不知所終。<br />\n<br />\n辯方說現在呈堂的首次會面錄影之前，其實警方已做了一輪會面，但盤問的警員不滿林的答案，故腰斬會面，而該警員沒有把錄影光碟交出保管，致光碟失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n周昨不同意辯方說法。辯方指光碟不會消失，問周有沒有辦法找回光碟觀看內容，周指沒辦法。辯方續指林從青山警署轉往屯門警署途中，負責盤問的警員在警車上威嚇林，逼他承認指控和按教導作供。周昨亦不同意。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCC408/16<br />\n■記者勞東來"},{"pid":"3b5c9b45d0ec74baf89289aea7ff54c7817481e1","tid":628836,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"嗱 香港警察呢"},{"pid":"c9e8145421bc30b2c15284c3c7fb969775759449","tid":628836,"uid":24044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"[black]香港警察[/black]"},{"pid":"ef30d961646562b998daddde9c86da4c6966a83e","tid":628836,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfa9dc66c5811cd4c2662ea1bf00d68b103e6601","tid":628836,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"狗賊變狗公安"},{"pid":"a6081f5662537321c2e1b2590d46edcc31123841","tid":628836,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}